<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />Yahweh takes notice of us and will bless us;</para>

<para style="q1">he will bless the family of Israel;</para>

<para style="q1">he will bless the family of Aaron.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />He will bless those who honor him,</para>

<para style="q1">both young and old.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />May Yahweh increase your numbers more and more,</para>

<para style="q1">yours and your descendants'.</para>
